ta remote behavior.\n   117\t- It does not add GitMeta APIs for scoped agentlog refs.\n   118\t- It does not add a remote flag or default to `origin`.\n   119\t- It does not call custom backend ingestion or product-specific sharing logic.\n   120\t- Simplicity is preferred over early isolation; revisit scoped sync only when a\n   121\t  concrete privacy, performance, or product requirement appears.\n   122\t\n   123\tUse [Agentlog Maintainability Playbook](maintainability-playbook.md) at useful\n   124\tcheckpoints, especially if sync grows beyond this small wrapper around GitMeta.\n","tool_name":null,"tool_input":null,"source_record":{"timestamp":"2026-05-11T19:50:27.671Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"function_call_output","call_id":"[REDACTED:entropy]"}}}